[[Discover Greenland Update]]
Small Update for the Event :)

[] Overall
- Added Predefined Positions/Frequencys for:
-- Airport | Position IVAO | Frequency | Station Name
-- BGBW | BGBW_I_TWR | 119.10 | Narsarsuaq AFIS
-- BGGH | BGGH_I_TWR | 119.10 | Nuuk AFIS
-- BGJN | BGJN_I_TWR | 119.10 | Ilulissat AFIS
-- BGPT | BGPT_I_TWR | 118.10 | Paamiut AFIS
-- BGMQ | BGMQ_I_TWR | 118.50 | Maniitsoq AFIS
-- BGSS | BGSS_I_TWR | 118.10 | Sisimiut AFIS
-- BGAA | BGAA_I_TWR | 118.50 | Aasiaat AFIS
-- BGSF |  BGSF_TWR  | 118.30 | Sondrestrom Tower
-- BGSF |  BGSF_APP  | 126.20 | Sondrestrom Approach
-- BGGL |  BGGL_CTR  | 121.30 | Nuuk Information
-- BGGL | BGGL_S_CTR | 121.30 | Nuuk Information (Sector South)
-- BGGL | BGGL_N_CTR | 120.30 | Nuuk Information (Sector North)

- (Note: Due to the way IVAO handles Voice Communication this is highly
suitable for Errors when multiple Controllers are connected due to "close" proximity
of stations with same Frequency.)

[] BGBW - Narsarsuaq
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Narsarsuaq TIZ (12nm Circle)

[] BGGH - Nuuk
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Nuuk TIZ (20nm Circle)

[] BGJN - Ilulissat
- Added GEO and FCL (thanks to Matthew)
- Added Ilulissat TIZ (20nm Circle)

[] BGPT - Paamiut
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Paamlut TIZ (20nm Circle)

[] BGMQ - Maniitsoq
- Added GEO and FCL
