[] BGSS - Sisimiut
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Sisimiut TIZ (20nm Circle)

[] BGAA - Aasiaat
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Aasiaat TIZ (20nm Circle)

[] BGSF - Kangerlussuaq
- Added GEO and FCL
- Added Taxiway Labels
- Added VFR Reporting Points
- Added LOC/NDB Approaches
- Added GA Procedure
- Added SF Holding Pattern

[] BIAR - Akureyri
- Adjusted All Departure Routes to be drawn accordingly
- Added AKI 2A/2B, AR-1A departure Routes
- [RWY19] Adjusted RNAV - now named RNP Y according to Charts
- [RWY19] RNP X added Line from FAF to Treshhold
- [STARs] Renamed "STARs (ILS)" to "STARs" since they Serves ILS and RNP Y
- [STARs] Added STAR Designators at first Waypoint
- [ATC] Changed ATC Positions in Sectorfile according to local procedures
-- [ATC] Disabled predefined BIAR_TWR Position
-- [ATC] Changed predefined BIAR_APP Frequency to 18.2
-- Need to talk to ATC Department how to handle this Station

Please get familiar with Akureyri Procedures since TWR/APP/AFIS is one Frequency/Position IRL.
Time | Position (Callsign):
0700-2300 (lcl) | TWR/APP (Akureyri Tower)
2300-0700 (lcl) | AFIS (Akureyri Radio)

[Future]
Changing the STAR Handling into an Overview Button and 
Single Arrival Routes accordingly for the possibility of better Text Communication.

[NOTE]
Due to overall Information slowly added into the Sectorfile please
get familiar with all the Filter Options available.
For further Questions feel free to contact me.

